thomas - named in honor of thomas fuchs, author or script.aculo.us, emile and scripty2
inspired by emile with the following additions
  - improvements to parsing engine
  - allows morphing between one or more classes
  - support for webkit transitions
  - chaining controls
  - additional timing functions
  
